{
  "texts": [
    "51 By adhering to these strategies, organizations can effectively leverage AI technologies in their publication work involving personal information, while also maintaining compliance with GDPR and HIPAA, ultimately fostering trust and safeguarding user privacy.",
    "Given that AI has the capability to enhance grammatical accuracy and provide relevant data, authors, editors, and readers need to be more vigilant about ensuring the trustworthiness and reliability of the information presented.",
    "A study suggests that enhancing public awareness of AI and robotic autonomous systems, along with their potential applications and usage contexts, will help manage expectations and address our inherent resistance to change.",
    "Additionally, the significant timesaving benefits of AI usage contribute greatly to its positive impact.",
    "52 Organizations like the European Commission's High-level Expert Group on AI (HLEG) have taken the stance that AI is a technology we can, and should, place our trust in."
  ]
}